{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:58:34.576936+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "---\n\n## Triage Summary\n\n**Issue #1: \"gwc push doesn't work — is this supported?\"**\n\n**Verdict: Not a bug — working as designed. Should be closed.**\n\nThe README is very clear that `gwc` intentionally does **not** support network operations:\n\n> *\"Network operations such as `push`, `pull`, `fetch`, and `clone` are intentionally out of scope; use plain `git` for those.\"*\n\nThis is reiterated in a dedicated **\"Not supported\"** section at the bottom of the README.\n\n**Recommended action:** Close as **not planned** (this is a feature request for something deliberately excluded from scope). Add a comment explaining that `gwc` is a local-only workflow companion and network ops should use `git` directly.\n\n**⚠️ Note:** I was unable to execute the close/comment via the API — the current GitHub token lacks the necessary permissions (`403 Resource not accessible by personal access token`). A maintainer with write access will need to perform the action manually.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 248, "prompt_tokens": 5630, "total_tokens": 5878, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 32, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 5120, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.000155176, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 8.5736e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 6.944e-05}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780873108-KPYPoC6l90ESMvgqJCTR", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea44f-1a36-71d1-91e8-cd426217e3ac-0", "tool_calls": [], "in